http://www.groupon.com/deals/tinas-ethiopian-cafe?fb_ref=anonymous&fb_source=profile_multiline  omg, tina's is open again... new location: Cooper Marketplace 785 W Warner Rd., Suite 103  Gilbert, Arizona 85233   get your groupons now!
