A stupid policy for an empty restaurant, I think, and if all else had been good I might have excused this annoying oddity.
At least they didn't require us to go outside and call in a reservation on our cell phone.
They gradually got off their butts and went to the kitchen, while leaving pizza boxes from their meal strewn about the restaurant.
